             was indicted for that he, on the <rs id="t18180114-91-cd487" type="crimeDate">13th of December</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180114-91-off488 t18180114-91-cd487"></join>, <rs id="t18180114-91-off488" type="offenceDescription">
